data.description: PRIVATE, PEACEFUL, SERENE. Located in the desirable Winter Gardens neighborhood of Bradenton. Surrounded by lush landscaping, mature trees, and an orchard, this 2 bed 2 bath, oversized 1 car garage, private pool home sits on 1/3 of an acre! Split floor plan with expansive rooms, living and kitchen areas. Master bedroom en-suite with walk-in closet. Brand new waterproof restortation oak laminate flooring throughout the home. The electrical switches, outlets and lighting have all been replaced new throughout. The exterior and interior was recently painted (2023). Plenty of room for entertaining. Bring your boat or RV...No HOA and No CDD fees here. Roof (2010). Newer A/C (2018) just serviced. Conveniently located to shopping, UTC Mall, restaurants, I-75 and award winning beaches. Come see and make this home yours today!
